name: Cult达人极限攀岩
description:
Use your skill to climb to the top!

You will control a cut climber with your own limbs, explore the carefully designed climbing wall, climb to a new height, and unlock the new clothes.

Master the simple and unique climbing mechanism, challenge you to master the gravity and test! Experience leisure fun!

Play as you like: you can get corresponding points in climbing, in exchange for more suits and equipment, and you can see all kinds of funny cut postures.
